 Z = 0\")))\ntext(x = 3, y = -0.8, expression(paste(\"Slope = \", beta[1])))\n\nsegments(-.9, b0, 0, b0, lty = 3)\nsegments(0, b0+b2, 0, -1, lty = 3)\n",
